## ================================
## Sample Requests for Testing
## Use with REST Client extension in VS Code
## or copy to curl/Postman
## ================================

### Health Check
GET https://localhost:5001/health

### ================================
### Send Chat Message (Non-Streaming)
### ================================
POST https://localhost:5001/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello, how are you?",
  "streamResponse": false
}

### ================================
### Send Chat Message with Existing Conversation
### ================================
POST https://localhost:5001/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "your-conversation-id-here",
  "message": "Tell me more about that",
  "streamResponse": false
}

### ================================
### Stream Chat Message
### ================================
POST https://localhost:5001/api/chat/stream
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Tell me a long story about AI"
}

### ================================
### Refresh Agent (Force Cache Update)
### ================================
POST https://localhost:5001/api/chat/refresh-agent

### ================================
### Chat Health Check
### ================================
GET https://localhost:5001/api/chat/health
